author: Robert Gearty
title: Virginia pastor who said ‘God is larger than this dreaded virus’ dies from coronavirus
description: The coronavirus has killed a prominent Virginia pastor who told his congregation at a service in March, “I firmly believe that God is larger than this dreaded virus.”
